Example .env file for smart-plant-advisor backend
Local SQLite development (fallback):
DB_URL=sqlite:///./local.db
Supabase PostgreSQL connection string:
You can paste the Supabase "postgres://..." URL here.
config.py will automatically convert postgres:// to postgresql+psycopg2://.
Example:
DB_URL=postgres://postgres:YOUR_PASSWORD@YOUR_HOST:5432/postgres?sslmode=require

# Supabase storage (required for image uploads)
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=YOUR_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
SUPABASE_PLANT_BUCKET=plant-images
SUPABASE_DREAM_BUCKET=dream-images
